                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13102998" author="jbellis" created="Mon, 12 Sep 2011 20:19:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is this related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3175&quot; title=&quot;Ec2Snitch nodetool issue after upgrade to 0.8.5&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3175&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3175&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13103007" author="brandon.williams" created="Mon, 12 Sep 2011 20:25:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13151540" author="alexaraujo" created="Wed, 16 Nov 2011 21:38:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merges 1.0&apos;s Ec2Snitch which does the right thing&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13151544" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 16 Nov 2011 21:46:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed.  Note that I think this is the preferable way to solve this, since it allows you to change snitches for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3114&quot; title=&quot;After Choosing EC2Snitch you can&amp;#39;t migrate off w/o a full cluster restart&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3114&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3114&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, though your consistency guarantees will likely be violated and require repair afterwards.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13151657" author="hudson" created="Thu, 17 Nov 2011 00:01:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Integrated in Cassandra-0.8 #399 (See &lt;a href=&quot;https://builds.apache.org/job/Cassandra-0.8/399/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://builds.apache.org/job/Cassandra-0.8/399/&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;br/&gt;
    Set default rack/dc in ec2snitch to avoid NPEs.&lt;br/&gt;
Patch by Alex Araujo, reviewed by brandonwilliams for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3186&quot; title=&quot;nodetool should not NPE when rack/dc info is not yet available&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3186&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3186&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

